dcterms:description: Prospector is a novel visual analytics system designed to help analysts better understand predictive models. It supports data scientists in evaluating predictive models not just based on accuracy but also on interpretability and actionable insights, leveraging the concept of partial dependence to communicate how features affect predictions.
dcterms:title: Prospector

dcterms:creator: Josua Krause
Adam Perer
Kenney Ng
dcterms:description: Class Signatures is a visual analytics workflow designed to interpret predictive associations between a large set of binary features and a binary target. It involves modeling predictive associations, increasing contrast, clustering examples, and ranking features to provide user-interpretable rules that explain predictions for different subgroups of data items.
dcterms:title: Class Signatures
